    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.28) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.28)) * 0.52)
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.27 - tmp + 0.37) / 0.33) * wp.exp((tmp + 0.20 + tmp + 0.52)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.00 - v1 + 0.36)) + ((v1 + 0.98 * v1 + 0.72) * (v1 + 0.01 - v0 + 0.48)))
    data[tid] = v0
